"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"The pupils of seeking knowledge release colorful hope, and the black fertile soil is full of lingering, impressively printed with \\\"emotional and rational analysis\\\". Yes, standing on the edge of the rainy season, the years of senior three are about to enter the melting pot of society, relying on intuition and emotional intimacy to understand this complex world, or logical analysis and rational judgment to promote the wings of rationality? I am willing to let life spray thin and quench my wings to capture the spiritual light of reason.\\n\\n \\n\\nBut can our childish hearts eliminate the entanglement of feelings and the disputes of love? So I lay alone on the reed.\\n\\n \\n\\nListen to the earnest teachings of our ancestors in the field -- Confucius dressed in a robe and shouted \\\"rationality first\\\" along the road; Zhuge killed Ma Su and reluctantly gave up his love. That's a promise, military discipline and rationality! Hemingway is alone in the sadness of the sea, Van Gogh is alone like a sunflower, ran? Jean was tortured all his life. Finally, considering the overall situation, he killed his lover to preserve secrets.\\n\\n \\n\\nWe can't write all the vicissitudes and events in our clarified eyes. We can't grow a wisdom without one thing. In order to learn from later teachers, we can have some insights and seek direction from classics, records and reality. From Stendhal's \\\"red and black\\\" and Tolstoy's \\\"Anna Karenina\\\", my fresh heart touched the protagonist's emotional and ethical, rational contradiction and distressing distress. It can reflect the shadow of real life. Embezzlers do not bend the law for personal gain as soon as they take office. Murderers and arsonists may be clinging to the injustice or protection of a relative. In the same sentence, a son is smart, and a neighbor is a dark room. Man is such a strange animal, but we should see the direction, learn to mature and try to grow up. Time flies like water. We should not only engrave the tears; The wind and rain are bad. We should always quench our wings.\\n\\n \\n\\n如果不是理性的爱国，关心国家和人民，蒋淑纯还会回到手术台上吗？叶欣会成为另一个夜莺节护士吗？David Ho将放弃对艾滋病鸡尾酒疗法的研究，离非典不远了。情感是一根树枝，也是一种润滑剂。情感的距离不会影响我们对事物的正确认识。理性永远是中坚力量和主流。否则，当代“孔繁森”郑培民怎能永远记住“不闯红灯”，伏明霞追击惊心动魄的弧线，张健告别年迈的父母穿越渤海海峡\\n\\n \\n\\n忘恩负义，看天上的云；我无意去或留下。愿庭前花开花落。我向太阳挥手，捕捉理性之光！\",\"timestamp\":1639147715,\"title\":\"LIGHT\"},\"digest\":\"pPKnEnCdNbUDQOvTVahDK6mar3F2lfavxfqgUHflMkU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x50b172f3974002501552d721A76E30A5532B7240\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"_L1chAxmGWJog1umyJ29hoRuBYlNxQ70WRSKe-WRigo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fN1vdGrSurUKDS9KATdeDNnt7T957YJJnwtPQRTXtJ8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"MsqNHoDGeTUiCqgr5pNs7nlzrzUuTLTROIgDaUM8cKNrdOSiMKjmRzC9ivZSsKgZtDNgsUJobDzt7Q16tFVzSQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x7230876ba1e39f3075fda9df3d55564cd72c7892e6ae40fba6f4997683fe1b252f5a064650ba8deaa4d3f40523159621709eb704f88b1a1487a45d82294143511b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"_L1chAxmGWJog1umyJ29hoRuBYlNxQ70WRSKe-WRigo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"fN1vdGrSurUKDS9KATdeDNnt7T957YJJnwtPQRTXtJ8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"pPKnEnCdNbUDQOvTVahDK6mar3F2lfavxfqgUHflMkU\"}"